content: odilitime: Merged 3 PRs this week, including a version bump (#3306), Docker and types fixes (#3220), and a develop-to-main merge (#3216), with substantial code changes totaling +91.5k/-53.8k lines across 1947 files. Demonstrated strong review activity with 19 PR reviews (13 approvals) and 74 PR comments while maintaining a moderately consistent work pattern across 4 days. Configuration files represented the majority (81%) of changes, with bug fixes accounting for 31% of the work focus.
